8... Bd6 9. Bxd6 Qxd6 10. d4 Qg6 11. Kf1 Bf5 12. c3 $14 {White keeps his extra
pawn}) 9. Ne2 Bd6 {this position was reached in the game So-Moussard, World
Cup 2023. Now I suggest to play} 10. Bxd6 Qxd6 11. exd4 {Engine shows 0.00,
but in a real game Black is the one who needs to know the precise moves} Nxd4 (
11... Bg4 $5 12. f3 O-O-O $1 {Engine shows 0.00, but in a real game Black is
the one who needs to know precise moves} 13. d5 $5 (13. fxg4 Nxd4 $13) 13...
Bxf3 (13... Qxd5 14. Nbc3 Qc5 $1 {[%emt 0:00:00] against} (14... Qe5 $2 15.
